verse = \lyricmode {
  See how all pass -- ers -- by have robbed and plun -- dered him;
he is his neigh -- bours' scorn, en -- dur -- ing bit -- ter shame.
The right hand of his foes you have in war ex -- alt -- ed;
they cheered in tri -- umph when a -- gainst him they re -- volt -- ed.
His sword you have turned back, his en -- e -- mies have felled him,
and in his ma -- ny bat -- tles you have not up -- held him.
}
